data.description: Location, Location, Location. A move-in ready, ranch-style home in the heart of J-Town. This home offers  3 spacious size bedrooms, 1.5 bath, separate utility room and a 2 car dethatched garage for plenty of extra storage. Fully fenced in back yard with lots of green space, great for the kids and dogs to run and play. Enjoy entertaining on the covered back porch.
